OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning in the west
OL,6,Fwith some light rain, dry and brighter
OL,7,Fin the east. Bright spells and a few
OL,8,Fshowers through the afternoon. Warm,
OL,9,Fparticularly in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain spreads northeast
OL,12,Fthrough the evening, heavy for a time.
OL,13,FBecoming largely dry overnight with
OL,14,Fclear spells in the east, but cloudy
OL,15,Fwith patchy light rain in the west.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FDry and warm with sunny
OL,18,Fspells in the east. Cooler in the west
OL,19,Fand cloudy to start but some bright
OL,20,Fspells developing during the day
OL,21,Fbefore some rain overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
